title: find your serenity today @ the wilcox...
posting_body: ['Welcome Home to The Wilcox', 'The Wilcox is a brand-new boutique community in the heart of downtown Ballard with thoughtfully designed amenity spaces and homes offering plenty of bright and open living space.', 'The apartments feature gorgeous finishes such as quartz countertops, high-end appliances, and tile backsplashes.', 'You can enjoy panoramic views of the Seattle skyline and Olympic Mountains atop the stunning roof deck.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 15', 'OR Text', '15', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to chat!', 'See our property details here:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 600 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Breakfast bars*', '- In-Home Full-size Washer & Dryer', '- USB ports', '- Key fob entry system', '- Wood Plank-Style Flooring', '- 9-10 Foot Ceilings', '- Pendant lighting*', '- Quartz Countertops', '- Energy Star Stainless Appliances', '- Two Stunning Color Palettes', '- Walk-in closet*', '- Programmable Thermostats', '- Keyless Fob Entry System', '- Modern Apartment Homes', 'Community Amenities', '- Work-From-Home Hubs w/WiFi', '- 24 Hour Fitness Studio', '- Resident Clubroom & Kitchen', '- Garage Parking', '- Social Rooftop Lounges & Grills', '- Dedicated Bike Storage', '- Rooftop Deck w/Panoramic Views', '- Rooftop Pet Sanctuary', '- Gaming Area w/Billiard and Pool', "- A 'Walker's Paradise' with a 97 WalkScore", 'Pet Policy', 'Dog and cat friendly', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Saturday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Sunday: 11:00AM-5:00PM', 'The Wilcox', '2003 NW 57th Street, Seattle, WA, 98107', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'DRiCT8Jl2D']
